2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong:
MLML 233:Adv Marine Ecol-  Selected topics and current issues in marine ecology. The subjects vary depending on student demand and availability of instructors. Can be repeated for credit when topics change. Offered through Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML); contact SEP program office for MLML registration procedures.

(Prereq: Exclude Freshmen and Sophomore and Junior)
